Description:
    Generate Bear's folder structure into your application and fill in
    the variables partial to easily customize Bear and also your main
    stylesheet file (application.css.scss).

Example:
    rails g bear:structure

    This will create the following folders:
      app/assets/stylesheets/components
      app/assets/stylesheets/layout
      app/assets/stylesheets/modules
      app/assets/stylesheets/responsive
      app/assets/stylesheets/settings
